<i>adverb</i>: 혹은 [호근], 혹 [혹], 왕왕 [왕ː왕], 때로 [때로], 간혹 [간ː혹], 간간이 [간ː가니], 가다가 [가다가], 가끔 [가끔] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>혹은 [호근]</dt><br>
<dd>1. or; if not</dd><br>
<dd>그렇지 않으면. 또는 그것이 아니면.</dd><br>
<dd>If not; or if it is not.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sometimes; from time to time</dd><br>
<dd>더러는.</dd><br>
<dd>Sometimes.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>혹 [혹]</dt><br>
<dd>1. by any chance</dd><br>
<dd>그러할 리는 없지만 만일에.</dd><br>
<dd>Not probably but possibly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. accidentally</dd><br>
<dd>어쩌다가 우연히.</dd><br>
<dd>By chance.</dd><br>
<dd>3. maybe</dd><br>
<dd>짐작대로 어쩌면.</dd><br>
<dd>Perhaps as one has guessed.</dd><br>
<dd>4. sometimes; occasionally; once in a while</dd><br>
<dd>어쩌다가 아주 가끔.</dd><br>
<dd>Sometimes at random intervals.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>왕왕 [왕ː왕]</dt><br>
<dd>sometimes; occasionally; now and then</dd><br>
<dd>시간의 간격을 두고 가끔.</dd><br>
<dd>From time to time, at intervals.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>때로 [때로]</dt><br>
<dd>1. occasionally</dd><br>
<dd>경우에 따라서.</dd><br>
<dd>Depending on the situation.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sometimes</dd><br>
<dd>이따금 한 번씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Once in a while.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>간혹 [간ː혹]</dt><br>
<dd>sometimes; occasionally; once in a while</dd><br>
<dd>어쩌다가 아주 가끔.</dd><br>
<dd>Rare and at random intervals.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>간간이 [간ː가니]</dt><br>
<dd>1. occasionally; sometimes; from time to time</dd><br>
<dd>시간적 간격을 두고 얼마쯤 있다가 가끔씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Once in a while with a certain time interval.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sparsely</dd><br>
<dd>공간적인 거리를 두고 여기저기에.</dd><br>
<dd>Here and there with a certain spatial interval.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가다가 [가다가]</dt><br>
<dd>sometimes; occasionally</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 계속하는 동안에 어쩌다가 가끔.</dd><br>
<dd>Every now and then while doing something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가끔 [가끔]</dt><br>
<dd>sometimes</dd><br>
<dd>어쩌다가 한 번씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Once in a while.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>